column1: Daily Weather Observations for Wagga Wagga, New South Wales for March 2021
Prepared at 16:00 UTC on Thursday  7 October 2021   IDCJDW2139.202103
Some cloud observations are from automated equipment; these are somewhat different to those made by a human observer and may not appear every day.
Observations were drawn from Wagga Wagga AMO {station 072150}
